https://docs.qameta.io/allure/

#1
2.1.4. Manual installation

    Download the latest version as zip archive from Maven Central - Download allure to local machine - https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2/io/qameta/allure/allure-commandline/

    Unpack the archive to allure-commandline directory.

    Navigate to bin directory.

    Use allure.bat for Windows or allure for other Unix platforms.

    Add allure to system PATH.

#2
    Rung Maven clean

#3
Generate allure report

    allure generate ./allure-results --clean


